- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes an efficient algorithm for clustering, which is a core topic in data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a machine learning algorithm for clustering, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper uses information-theoretic concepts such as entropy and mutual information to analyze the performance of the algorithm.
